<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>Neervet Animal Clinic</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="img/logo.png">
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js" integrity="sha256-/xUj+3OJU5yExlq6GSYGSHk7tPXikynS7ogEvDej/m4=" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-ggOyR0iXCbMQv3Xipma34MD+dH/1fQ784/j6cY/iJTQUOhcWr7x9JvoRxT2MZw1T" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">
    <script src='js/printThis.js'></script>
    <script src="js/myscript.js"></script>
    
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-default">
        <div id='logo'></div>
        <a class="navbar-brand disable-select" id='to-dashboard' href="/home">Neervet Animal Clinic</a>
        <div id='user-nav'>
            <p class='lead disable-select'>Welcome, </p>
            <a class='text-info dropdown-toggle disable-select' id='userDropdown' role='button' data-toggle='dropdown'><%= username%> <span id='username'> (<%= userlevel %>)</span></a>
            <ul class='dropdown-menu' aria-labelledby="userDropdown">
                <li> <a id='edit-profile' class="dropdown-item disable-select" href="/editProfile">Edit Profile</a></li>
                <li> <a class="dropdown-item disable-select" href="/logout">Logout</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <!-- <div id='user-logout'>
            <a class='lead' href='/logout'>Logout</a>
        </div> -->
    </nav>

    <div id='container' class="container-fluid">
        
        <div id='sidenav'>
            <div id='navigation'>
                <ul>
                    
                    <!-- <a class='sub-name'>USER LOGGED</a>
                    <li class='sub-menu'>
                        <a id='admin' class='lead'><img src='img/profile.png'><span><%= username %></span><img id='down-arrow' src='img/down-arrow.png'></a>
                        <ul>
                            <li><a id='edit-profile' href='/editProfile'><img src='img/edit.png'>Edit Profile</a></li>
                            <li><a id='manage-user' href='/manageUser'><img src='img/manage.png'>Manage User</a></li>
                        </ul>
                    </li> -->
                    <a class='sub-name disable-select'>SYSTEM</a>
                    <li><a id='dashboard' class='lead disable-select' href='/home'><img src='img/dashboard.png'>Dashboard</a></li>
                    <li><a id='manage-user' class='lead disable-select' href='/manageUser'><img src='img/profile.png'>Manage User</a></li>
                    <li><a id='client' class='lead clients disable-select' href='/client'><img src='img/clients.png'>Manage Clients</a></li>
                    <li><a id='appointment' class='lead disable-select' href='/appointment' ><img src='img/appointment.png'>Appointments</a></li>
                    <a class='sub-name'>UTILITY</a>
                    <li><a id='backup-restore' class='lead disable-select' href='/backuprestore'><img src='img/database.png'>Backup/Restore</a></li>
                    <li id='help' class=' disable-select' data-toggle="modal" data-target="#helpModal" ><a>Help <img src='img/question.png'></a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
        </div>
        <div id='main' class=' disable-select'>
            <h1 class='display-4'>Dashboard</h1>
            <div id='main-top'>
                <div id='staff' class='main-box'>
                    <img src='img/people.png' class='icon'>
                    <p class='lead lead-num'><%= staff[0].staff %></p>
                    <p class='lead lead-name'>Staff</p>
                </div>
                
                <div id='clients' class='main-box clients'>
                    <img src='img/people.png' class='icon'>
                    <p class='lead lead-num'><%= clients[0].clients %></p>
                    <p class='lead lead-name'>Clients</p>
                </div> 
                
                <div id='appointments-today' class='main-box'>
                    <input type='hidden' id='app-today' href='/appointmentsToday'>
                    <img src='img/apptoday.png' class='icon'>
                    <p class='lead lead-num'><%= app[0].apps %></p>
                    <p class='lead lead-name'>Appointments Today</p>
                </div>  

            </div>
            
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- HELP MODAL -->
<div class="modal fade  disable-select" id="helpModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="helpModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog modal-xl modal-dialog-scrollable" role="document">
      <div class="modal-content">
        <div class="modal-header">
          <h5 class="modal-title" id="helpModalLabel">Help</h5>
          <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
            <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
          </button>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-body">
            <div id='how-to-nav'>
                <div id="list-example" class="list-group">
                    <a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action" value='list-item-1'>How to Add Client</a>
                    <a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action" value="list-item-2">How to Add Pet</a>
                    <a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action" value="list-item-3">How to Add Record</a>
                    <a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action" value="list-item-4">How to Print Report</a>
                    <a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action" value="list-item-5">How to Add Appointment</a>
                    <a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action" value="list-item-6">How to Send Notification</a>
                    <a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action" value="list-item-7">How to Backup </a>
                    <a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action" value="list-item-8">How to Restore</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div id='how-to-main'>
                <h2 class='display-4'>Guides</h2>
           
                <div data-spy="scroll" data-target="#list-example" data-offset="0" class="scrollspy-example">
                    <h4 id="list-item-1" class='lead'>How to Add Client</h4>
                    <p>Go to Dashboard -> Clients -> Select <button class='btn btn-primary btn-sm'>Add</button> at the top right corner -> Fill up the form with client's data <br> -> Select <button class='btn btn-primary btn-sm'>Add Client</button></p>
                    <p>Or</p>
                    <p>Go to Manage Clients -> Select <button class='btn btn-primary btn-sm'>Add</button> at the top right corner-> Fill up the form with client's data <br>-> Select <button class='btn btn-primary btn-sm'>Add Client</button> </p>

                    <h4 id="list-item-2" class='lead'>How to Add Pet</h4>
                    <p>Go to Manage Clients -> Select Client -> Select <button class='btn btn-primary btn-sm'>+ Pet</button> -> Enter Pet data -> Select Add </p>

                    <h4 id="list-item-3" class='lead'>How to Add Record</h4>
                    <p>Go to Manage Clients -> Select Client -> Select Pet -> Select '+ Record' -> Enter Pet Record data <br>-> Select <button class='btn btn-primary btn-sm'>Add</button> </p><br>
                    <p>To add pet, Go <a href="#list-item-2">Here</a></p>
                    
                    <h4 id="list-item-4" class='lead'>How to Print Report</h4>
                    <p>Go to Pet's page -> Select <button class='btn btn-primary btn-sm'>View Report</button> -> Select <button class='btn btn-primary btn-sm'>Print</button></p>

                    <h4 id="list-item-5" class='lead'>How to Add Appointment</h4>
                    <p>Go to Client's page -> Select <button class='btn btn-primary btn-sm'>+ Appointment</button></p>

                    <h4 id="list-item-6" class='lead'>How to Send Notification</h4>
                    <p>Go to Appointments -> Select <button class='btn btn-outline-success btn-sm'>Notification</button> -> Select <button class='btn btn-primary btn-sm'>Send Notification</button></p>

                    <h4 id="list-item-7" class='lead'>How to Backup</h4>
                    <p>Go to Backup / Restore -> Select <button class='btn btn-info btn-sm'>Backup Now</button> -> Select file directory to download</p>

                    <h4 id="list-item-8" class='lead'>How to Restore</h4>
                    <p>Go to Backup / Restore -> Select 'Choose file' -> Select file -> Select <button class='btn btn-info btn-sm'>Restore Now</button></p>

                </div>
            </div>
            
        </div>
        <div class="modal-footer">
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
</div>
    

    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-JjSmVgyd0p3pXB1rRibZUAYoIIy6OrQ6VrjIEaFf/nJGzIxFDsf4x0xIM+B07jRM" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>